ğŸ“Œ PRODUCT REQUIREMENTS DOCUMENT (PRD)
Medical Store Web Application
ğŸ§  1. Product Overview
Vision

Build an online pharmacy platform where users can:

Browse medicine products

Upload prescriptions

Add to cart and checkout

Place orders

Admin manages inventory and orders

This system will follow the design and structure pattern of your DoctorAppointment repository.

ğŸ§‘â€ğŸ’» 2. User Roles
Role	Capabilities
Guest User	Browse products, view details, register
Registered User	Order medicines, upload prescriptions, view orders
Admin	Manage products, orders, users, prescriptions
ğŸ—ºï¸ 3. Features & User Stories
ğŸ§¾ 3.1 Authentication

Description: Users must register and login to place orders.

User Stories:

As a user, I want to register using email + password.

As a user, I want to login/logout securely.

Requirements:

Django Auth integration

User detail validation

Bootstrap-based forms

ğŸ’Š 3.2 Product Catalog

Description: Users can view and browse medicine listings.

User Stories:

As a user I want to view all products.

As a user I want to search products by name.

Requirements:

Product list page

Search bar (JS + backend filtering)

Medicine details page

ğŸ›’ 3.3 Cart Management

Description: Users can add products to a cart before checkout.

User Stories:

As a user I want to add medicine to cart.

As a user I want to view cart total and update quantities.

Requirements:

Cart view page

Update & remove items

Persist cart in session or DB

ğŸ“„ 3.4 Prescription Upload

Description: Some products require prescription upload.

User Stories:

As a user I want to upload prescription.

As admin I want to review and approve prescriptions.

Requirements:

Prescription upload form

File type validation

Admin approval workflow

ğŸ’³ 3.5 Checkout & Orders

Description: Users will place orders from the cart.

User Stories:

As a user I want to enter delivery address.

As a user I want to see order confirmation.

Requirements:

Address form in checkout

Order items stored in DB

Order confirmation page

ğŸ§‘â€ğŸ’¼ 3.6 Admin Dashboard

Description: Admin manages products, orders, users.

User Stories:

As admin I want to add/edit/delete products.

As admin I want to update order status.

Requirements:

Admin views for products

Order status change UI

Prescription management

